Jesse White (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesse_White_(actor) 0 Jesse White (born Jonah Marcus Weidenfeld, January 3, 1917 – January 9, 1997) was an American character actor. He is best remembered for having portrayed the Maytag repairman in television commercials from 1967 to 1988.
